bio.openEndedText: Hey there!  I'm a Nashville native that enjoys roller skating and trying new places to eat.  I hope to provide you with an awesome experience while exploring Nashville.  Thank you again for your support!

Don’t over pay for a base model vehicle at a rental car agency when you can ride in luxury or well equipped vehicle. All of my vehicles come equipped with the amenities you desire.
Reach out to me if you have any questions or concerns!

• Car girl 💁🏼‍♀️ World Traveler 🌎 ✈️ 
• 6 Year All-Star & Power Host
• Business Class Host (luxury vehicles)

Guest experience is my top priority! Whether you’re a 1st time Turo Guest or a Veteran, you receive my world class customer service, direct contact information, timely responses and someone who values your business.

Howdy car sharing community! We appreciate your interest in our cars. Cars have always been our passion and we're glad to share ours with responsible folks like yourself. We are a Turo Power Host and All Star Host with over 1900 customer satisfied trips hosted across various well maintained fully Electric Vehicles and even the latest brand new luxurious Cadillac Lyriq EV with Super Cruise self driving feature with automatic lane changes, similar to Tesla’s Navigate on autopilot feature as well as the 7 seater Rivian R1S Quad motor SUV. Kindly favorite our cars to help you find them easily in the future. Feel free to reach out to us by text or phone at 609 668 9012 if you have any questions before your booking or can’t find a specific car you are looking to book and we can get you in something similar or hopefully even better.

Hello! Welcome to our fleet! 

-We are Nashville’s top-rated host, and strive for 100% excellence. 

-With over 1500+ trips, we are committed to the 5-Star experience. Our team is dedicated to our customers, and will leave no stone unturned to give you the best car rental experience possible!

MEET OUR TEAM!

-DREW: Owner/Manager - Drew is a full time musician who enjoys playing drums around town behind various artists. He went to school at Belmont, and studied drum set through the percussion program. He is an avid Vintage VW enthusiast, and enjoys spending time with his Great Dane, Scrappy.

-ELIJAH: General Manager - Elijah is also a full time musician and drummer who plays around town frequently. He studied at Vol State, MTSU and Belmont University. He enjoys playing drums and spending weekends with his family,

ROBERT: Shift lead - Robert is a Nashville native who also works around town as an audio engineer. He enjoys traveling, surfing and playing guitar in his free time!

REBECCA: Shift lead - Rebecca is a Nashville native who graduated from Vanderbilt with a degree in Musical Composition. On her days off, you can catch her around town singing on many of Nashvilles hot stages! Rebecca enjoys spending time with her dog, Sparks, as well as spending time with friends. 

-Be sure to check out all of our awesome vehicles!

-We are conveniently located near downtown, only 11 minutes from the airport. 

-Don’t hesitate to reach out and ask us any questions you may have!

Hey there, welcome to Music City Wheels, where every ride is a melody! This is going to be fun!

At Music City Wheels, we're all about making your journey through the United States a memorable one. Our crew is here to ensure every aspect of your trip is on point. 

Step in, and you'll feel the enthusiasm we bring to providing top-notch service. Our drivers are friendly, knowledgeable, and ready to make your ride enjoyable. Yes, we take each trip very seriously. Whether it's giving directions, chatting, or where to take the cars, we're here to make your journey a good time. Most of the time that is to Gatlinburg! Ha.

We take pride in keeping our wheels in top shape for a safe and comfy experience. Clean rides, well-maintained, and stylish – because your trip with us is not just a commute, it's a cool experience. They smell GREAT!

Can't wait to host you!

My goal is to provide the best client experience with my fleet of economy and high end cars. With over four years experience on Turo, you'll find in my many reviews that I am very responsive, accessible and flexible with my guests; message or call me anytime. Personally I am passionate about cars and I love chatting with my guest about their cars and driving experience.
Our lot is a few minutes away from the Nashville International Airport (BNA) and offer  airport and custom delivery, long-term rentals, and repeat customer discounts.

::::::::::ATTENTION RENTER::::::::::
I take great pride in keeping my cars cleaned and SANITIZED. Every car is sanitized and cleaned thoroughly with anti-bacterial before and after each trip. Rest assured you are driving the world's cleanest germ free rental car on the market! I also regularly maintain all of my vehicles to ensure you have the safest trip possible!

::::::::::Required by Host::::::::::
-Valid Driver's License

Turo's new contactless handoffs available and the following items are mandatory before picking up the car:

﻿﻿﻿Please upload a photo of your drivers license to trip photos
﻿﻿﻿Please upload a photo of yourself holding your license

You can upload these photos by going to your reservation page scrolling down and where it says
"add photos" tap there to upload.

Hello!

My name is Ben and I have been a Nashville resident for over 2 years. Throughout my time in Nashville, I have had the benefit to meet hundreds of tourists looking to visit Nashville and surrounding areas and have shared their frustration on how long it takes to rent a vehicle at the Airport. In the last year I have aimed to create a small fleet of rentals outside of by 9-5 job with the mission to provide a seamless rental experience. By renting a car with me you are guaranteed to spend less than 15 minutes to check in and be on your way, have immediate communication for any questions/concerns, and most importantly a cool car! My cars were purposely selected so you could get something different from typical boring large company fleets.  

If you have any questions/comments feel free to text me at [Number redacted for privacy and security] and I will message you back promptly! 

Have an amazing day.

My love for cars got me on Turo and I am excited to rent my car out to you. I love to travel, meet people and try new restaurants. 

Are you new on Turo and have questions, I would happy to help!!!

My name is Dom. I am based out of Nashville and here to provide transportation to locals and tourists throughout the Middle Tennessee region. My goal is to provide consistent, quality service and make your experience as smooth and convenient as possible. Looking forward to being of service to you!

⭐️Hello there, I'm Tom, your friendly Turo host from Franklin, TN, and let me introduce you to our fantastic family car rental service. As a proud father of five and a dedicated family man, I understand the importance of safe, reliable, and comfortable transportation for your loved ones. Allow me to provide you with a top-notch Turo experience.

🚗Our family-owned fleet of vehicles is carefully selected to cater to all your travel needs, whether it's a weekend getaway or an extended family road trip. Each vehicle is meticulously maintained to ensure your safety and peace of mind on the road.

🧼When you rent with us, you're not just getting a car; you're getting a worry-free journey. Our commitment to excellence means you can trust that your rental will be clean, well-maintained, and ready to hit the road when you are.

🎸We take pride in our role as trusted Turo hosts, and we're here to make your travel experience smooth and enjoyable. Need recommendations for family-friendly destinations or travel tips? Just ask! We're more than happy to share our insights to help you make the most of your trip.

🚘Whether it's a weekend adventure with the kids or a romantic getaway with your partner, our family-oriented approach ensures you have the perfect vehicle for your needs.

✅Book with us today and experience the convenience, reliability, and personal touch that only a family host can provide. Your journey starts here, with Tom and the family, and we can't wait to serve you.

Through our partnership with Turo, we bring a level of professionalism and expertise that sets us apart. Our vehicles are meticulously maintained and meticulously inspected to ensure the highest standards of safety and quality for our customers.

Whether you're a leisure traveler exploring new destinations or a business professional on the go, Easy Car Rentals Inc on Turo offers a tailored solution to meet your specific needs. Our diverse fleet includes a wide range of vehicles, from economical options for budget-conscious travelers to premium vehicles for those seeking a touch of luxury.

At Easy Car Rentals Inc, we prioritize the satisfaction of our customers above all else. Our dedicated team of professionals is committed to providing personalized assistance and support throughout the rental process. Whether it's offering recommendations, addressing inquiries, arranging delivery logistics, or ensuring a smooth rental experience from start to finish, we go above and beyond to exceed our customers' expectations.

Experience Easy Car Rentals Inc on Turo Today:

Discover the difference of renting with Easy Car Rentals Inc on Turo. Join us today and experience the professionalism, reliability, and convenience that have made us a preferred choice among discerning travelers. With Easy Car Rentals Inc, your journey begins with ease.
